491
00:35:28,520 --> 00:35:29,520
tapos...

492
00:35:30,040 --> 00:35:31,160
ilang tao...

493
00:35:31,960 --> 00:35:33,320
ibubully ako.

494
00:35:33,560 --> 00:35:34,920
Sino ba ang may lakas ng loob na i-bully ka?

495
00:35:34,960 --> 00:35:36,280
Ako na ang unang tadtarin sa kanya.

496
00:35:39,560 --> 00:35:41,400
Natatakot ako kung alam mo kung sino ito,

497
00:35:41,880 --> 00:35:43,680
hindi mo kayang gawin yun.

498
00:35:57,200 --> 00:35:58,200
ano?

499
00:35:58,360 --> 00:36:00,360
Bakit hindi mo kasama si Guo Cheng Yu?

500
00:36:01,280 --> 00:36:02,280
WHO?

501
00:36:02,480 --> 00:36:03,480
Guo Cheng Yu.

502
00:36:04,480 --> 00:36:05,880
I think bagay kayong dalawa.

503
00:36:06,840 --> 00:36:07,840
Hindi bababa sa...

504
00:36:08,520 --> 00:36:10,040
mas mahusay kaysa sa iyo at kay Wang Shuo.

505
00:36:12,800 --> 00:36:14,160
Hindi ka pa rin magbehave, di ba?

506
00:36:15,800 --> 00:36:16,999
muli?

507
00:36:17,000 --> 00:36:18,040
Ikaw...

508
00:36:19,800 --> 00:36:21,080
Hindi ka pa rin mag-aasal.

509
00:36:22,720 --> 00:36:23,720
Itigil mo na.

510
00:36:28,200 --> 00:36:30,720
Ang mga unang sintomas
ng schizophrenia...

511
00:36:31,200 --> 00:36:33,720
ay paranoya,
matinding pagbabago sa personalidad,

512
00:36:34,080 --> 00:36:35,160
at neurasthenia.

513
00:36:36,520 --> 00:36:38,679
Ang mga salik na nakakaimpluwensya
ay biyolohikal,

514
00:36:38,680 --> 00:36:40,759
kapaligiran, at sikolohikal.

515
00:36:40,760 --> 00:36:42,439
pasensya na po. Ito ay kagyat.

516
00:36:42,440 --> 00:36:43,720
Paki-dismiss muna ang klase mo.

517
00:36:43,760 --> 00:36:45,000
- Okay?
- Tayo na.

518
00:36:45,400 --> 00:36:46,400
Halika na.

519
00:36:46,401 --> 00:36:48,401
- Xiao Shuai, isa kang doktor.
- Sinasanay ko sila.

520
00:36:49,000 --> 00:36:51,281
Suriin ito. Ito ang medical record ni Wang Shuo
noon.

521
00:36:51,640 --> 00:36:52,840
Pag-aralan ito para sa akin.

522
00:36:54,520 --> 00:36:56,640
"Bipolar disorder."

523
00:36:57,200 --> 00:36:58,280
"Malubhang pagkabalisa."

524
00:37:00,560 --> 00:37:02,160
Ang taon na naghiwalay kami ni Meng Tao,

525
00:37:02,400 --> 00:37:03,760
Nagkaroon din ako ng mga katulad na sintomas.

526
00:37:04,360 --> 00:37:05,360
Darn it.

527
00:37:05,640 --> 00:37:07,840
Mas malala pa ang kalagayan ni Wang Shuo kaysa sa akin.

528
00:37:10,880 --> 00:37:13,000
Ano ang mga sintomas
ng mga sakit na ito?

529
00:37:14,920 --> 00:37:16,200
Karaniwan silang nagpapakita ng...

530
00:37:16,280 --> 00:37:18,320
bilang mga alternating episode
ng depression at mania.

531
00:37:18,760 --> 00:37:20,240
Sa malalang kaso, mayroong...

532
00:37:20,480 --> 00:37:23,760
pandinig na guni-guni, maling akala,
at hindi maayos na pag-uugali.

533
00:37:24,520 --> 00:37:26,679
Sa madaling salita,
maaaring nagawa ni Wang Shu...

534
00:37:26,680 --> 00:37:28,600
ilang mga extreme na bagay noon
dahil doon.

535
00:37:30,360 --> 00:37:31,400
Pwede naman.

536
00:37:34,560 --> 00:37:35,560
bakit ka nandito?

537
00:37:40,840 --> 00:37:41,840
Para makita siya.

538
00:37:43,720 --> 00:37:45,920
Teka. Bakit mo siya pinuntahan?

539
00:37:46,560 --> 00:37:47,560
Hindi mo alam, di ba?

540
00:37:47,960 --> 00:37:50,360
Sobrang close na namin ngayon.

541
00:37:50,960 --> 00:37:51,960
Sabay pa kaming natulog.

542
00:37:53,080 --> 00:37:54,999
ano? Kailan ito nangyari?

543
00:37:55,000 --> 00:37:56,200
Bakit hindi mo sinabi sa akin?

544
00:37:57,640 --> 00:37:58,720
Noong araw na iyon...

545
00:37:59,080 --> 00:38:01,040
Huwag sabihin kay Xiao Shuai ang lahat
sa hinaharap.

546
00:38:01,800 --> 00:38:04,320
Paano kung ipagkanulo ka niya
at sabihin sa akin ang tungkol sa kanila balang araw?

547
00:38:09,600 --> 00:38:10,600
ayos lang.

548
00:38:10,680 --> 00:38:11,880
Hindi naman ako kailangan dito diba?

549
00:38:12,400 --> 00:38:13,920
Magsaya kayong dalawa. aalis na ako.

550
00:38:14,800 --> 00:38:15,840
Hoy, Da Wei!

551
00:38:15,880 --> 00:38:17,640
huwag kang pumunta! Da Wei.

552
00:38:23,400 --> 00:38:24,600
Tingnan mo si Da Wei.

553
00:38:25,000 --> 00:38:26,440
Napaka-petty niya.

554
00:38:27,000 --> 00:38:28,120
Tama na.

555
00:38:28,720 --> 00:38:31,200
Itigil ang pagpapanggap.
Masasabi ko kung ano ang iyong ginagawa.

556
00:38:44,280 --> 00:38:45,280
Wu Suo Wei.

557
00:38:46,320 --> 00:38:47,320
Laro tayo.

558
00:38:58,320 --> 00:38:59,320
Subukan muli.

559
00:39:01,600 --> 00:39:02,600
Kaya mo bang mag-dunk?

560
00:39:11,360 --> 00:39:14,080
Darn, ang galing.

561
00:39:14,480 --> 00:39:15,920
Napaka-cool ng rebound na iyon.

562
00:39:24,680 --> 00:39:25,800
Kahanga-hanga ka.

563
00:39:27,440 --> 00:39:28,520
Paano mo nagawa iyon?

564
00:39:30,320 --> 00:39:31,480
Turuan kita kung paano mag-dunk.

565
00:39:32,000 --> 00:39:33,800
Tuturuan mo ako?
Hindi ko akalain na matututunan ko ito.

566
00:39:46,680 --> 00:39:47,880
Paano mo nalaman na nandito ako?

567
00:39:49,120 --> 00:39:50,440
Hindi ako nagpunta dito para sayo.

568
00:39:51,880 --> 00:39:52,880
Ibigay mo siya sa akin.

569
00:39:56,480 --> 00:39:57,480
Ibalik mo siya.

570
00:39:58,880 --> 00:40:00,760
Sana ako ay Green-Eyed Monster,

571
00:40:01,240 --> 00:40:02,800
para ma-spoil mo ako
ng pitong segundo.

572
00:40:03,640 --> 00:40:05,240
Ikaw mismo ang gumawa ng lahat ng iyon.

573
00:40:05,520 --> 00:40:06,600
Hindi mo masisisi ang sinuman.

574
00:40:08,480 --> 00:40:09,480
Oo.

575
00:40:11,000 --> 00:40:12,000
mura ako.

576
00:40:12,120 --> 00:40:13,200
walanghiya ako.

577
00:40:13,280 --> 00:40:14,280
Deserve ko to.

578
00:40:14,920 --> 00:40:15,920
masaya ka na ba ngayon?

579
00:40:18,760 --> 00:40:19,760
ano ka...

580
00:40:20,000 --> 00:40:21,480
walang kinalaman sa akin.

581
00:40:24,560 --> 00:40:26,160
Bakit may sinabi kang
napakasakit?

582
00:40:27,200 --> 00:40:28,719
Magkaklase kami kung tutuusin.

583
00:40:28,720 --> 00:40:30,120
Kami ay magkasama sa napakaraming taon.

584
00:40:30,440 --> 00:40:31,440
Halimaw na may berdeng mata...

585
00:40:31,800 --> 00:40:33,160
parang anak natin.

586
00:40:33,960 --> 00:40:35,200
Sobrang close kami.

587
00:40:35,640 --> 00:40:37,200
Pwede ba wag mo akong ipahiya?

588
00:40:45,360 --> 00:40:46,400
Ibalik mo siya sa akin.

589
00:40:50,280 --> 00:40:52,960
Tingnan mo.
Ayaw ni Green-Eyed Monster na magkahiwalay tayo.

590
00:40:54,760 --> 00:40:55,840
Kung ganoon,

591
00:40:56,160 --> 00:40:57,880
dalhin mo ako sa snake farm.

592
00:40:58,200 --> 00:41:01,040
Balita ko maraming
ahas na iniwan ko kanina.

593
00:41:02,160 --> 00:41:04,600
Napakaraming taon na akong hiwalay sa aking laman at dugo.

594
00:41:04,840 --> 00:41:06,360
Oras na para bisitahin ko sila.

595
00:41:07,840 --> 00:41:09,320
Okay, Chi Cheng?

596
00:41:09,640 --> 00:41:10,640
Dalhin mo ako doon.

597
00:41:10,720 --> 00:41:11,880
pasensya na po. Sandali lang.

598
00:41:15,880 --> 00:41:18,280
Ang tagal ko na silang hindi nakikita.
Miss na miss ko na sila.

599
00:41:19,320 --> 00:41:21,040
I wonder kung kumakain sila ng maayos.

600
00:41:56,320 --> 00:41:57,400
Halimaw na may berdeng mata.

601
00:41:58,920 --> 00:42:00,760
(Hongshan Hospital)

602
00:42:01,800 --> 00:42:03,280
Hello, ikaw ba ang pamilya ni Zhang Li Ya?

603
00:42:03,360 --> 00:42:05,279
Walang sapat na pera
para sa pagpapaospital ni Zhang Li Ya.

604
00:42:05,280 --> 00:42:06,439
Mangyaring pumunta at magbayad ngayon.

605
00:42:06,440 --> 00:42:07,816
Huwag ipagpaliban ang kanyang nutrisyon
at paggamot.

606
00:42:07,840 --> 00:42:09,720
Okay. pasensya na po.

607
00:42:10,080 --> 00:42:11,640
humihingi ako ng tawad. Pupunta ako doon.

608
00:42:13,480 --> 00:42:14,480
pasensya na po.

609
00:42:19,840 --> 00:42:20,840
Lumabas ka.

610
00:42:20,880 --> 00:42:22,280
Mayroon akong mga kagyat na bagay na dapat asikasuhin.

611
00:42:23,480 --> 00:42:24,480
Lumabas ka.

612
00:43:49,200 --> 00:43:50,480
Bakit ka nakaupo sa ulan?

613
00:43:53,400 --> 00:43:54,680
Nakaupo ako dito...

614
00:43:56,640 --> 00:43:58,120
at umuulan lang.

615
00:43:59,640 --> 00:44:00,640
Hindi ko naman kasalanan.

616
00:44:01,200 --> 00:44:02,360
Saka bakit hindi ka umalis?

617
00:44:04,960 --> 00:44:07,360
Umuulan kung saan-saan.
Saan ako dapat pumunta?

618
00:44:15,200 --> 00:44:16,320
kapatid mo...

619
00:44:17,280 --> 00:44:18,600
kinuha ang aking Green-Eyed Monster.

620
00:44:23,440 --> 00:44:24,440
Tara na.

621
00:44:24,960 --> 00:44:26,040
Babawi ako sayo.

622
00:44:34,480 --> 00:44:35,560
(Bonus Clip)

623
00:44:39,720 --> 00:44:41,720
(Rekord na Medikal, Pangalan: Wang Shuo)
